<p><a href="#sdfootnote3anc" name="sdfootnote3sym">3</a><span> Cf.</span><span> Hans Blumenberg, </span><span><em>Schiffbruch mit Zuschauer</em></span><span> (Frankfurt am Main: Suhrkamp Verlag, 1997).</span></p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote4anc" name="sdfootnote4sym">4</a><span> </span><span>Lucretius, </span><span><em>On the Nature of the Universe</em></span><span>, trans. R. E. Latham (London: Penguin Books, 1994), 38.</span></p>
